items.name: Music Hub
items.title: Music Hub
items.headline: Welcome to the Music Wiki!
items.desc:
The Music Wiki is a wiki devoted to creating the definitive music encyclopedia which includes aspects of all music topics.

From artists to labels, to the songs themselves we are a resource for every aspect of the music business. All genres! All artists! All sounds! Whatever your preference, we aim to provide the definitive subculture soundtrack.

items.name: High School Musical Wiki
items.title: High School Musical Wiki
items.headline: High School Musical Wikia
items.desc: Welcome to High School Musical Wikia! The High School Musical Wikia is dedicated to the High School Musical franchise that follows a group of students at East High School as they make their way through drama, first loves, competition, and singing! The High School Musical franchise is one of Disney's most successful movie series and is still popular to this day! Enter now to learn more!

items.title: Long Island Music Scene Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Long Island Music Scene Wikia
items.desc:
The wiki about the history of the Long Island Music Scene that anyone can edit.

Wikia is a website that hosts User Generated Communities that can revolve around many different genres, including entertainment, video games, and lifestyle.  Everyone is invited to participate and edit, and anyone can create their very ow wiki about the topic of their choice.

items.name: Music Video Wiki
items.title: Music Video Wiki
items.headline: Learn about the evolution of music videos at Music Video Wiki
items.desc:
Music Video Wiki is about history of music videos, and the artists and the directors who helped influence the evolution of music videos.

Currently, Music Video Wiki contains over 2,000 articles on music videos with embedded videos from YouTube, Dailymotion and other video web sites, along with artists, directors and video concepts.
